The Burbank Portfolio App is designed for cutting edge Workplaces and Office Buildings that wish to provide their teams and tenants with high tech convenience that today’s world expects. The Burbank Portfolio App takes complex, time-consuming and repetitive building operations, streamlines them into always on, in the palm of your hand tech for Management, Staff and Tenants.

Rise Office provides:

- Fitness Reservations
- Visitor/Delivery Access Control
- Package Delivery, Notification and Tracking
- Work Order Management
- Reservations Management
- Valet Tracking and Notification
- Contact Management
- Building Newsfeed
- Document Vault
